{"title":"吝啬的人朋友远","authors":["郝苏民"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":12,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"吝啬的人朋友远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（蒙古谚语）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"懈惰的马路程远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吝啬的人朋友远。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为财而生，不如为众而死。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱朋友如胜过生命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵然死去还有生命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郝苏民辑译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}